Package: devtoolverse
Title: Easily Install and Load Select Packages
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
  person(
  given = "Indrajeet", 
  family = "Patil", 
  email = "patilindrajeet.science@gmail.com", 
  role = c("aut", "cre"), 
  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1995-6531"))
  )
Description: The 'devtoolverseverse' is selection of packages designed to be loaded
    in concert. The purpose of this package is to make it easy to install and 
    subsequently load packages needed for development of R packages.
URL: https://github.com/IndrajeetPatil/devtoolverse
